snippet.description:
Such a powerful activation from Mira, here it is again:

We are delighted to give you this exercise which should help you move through this deep fatigue; you will need a crystal of your choice at this time. Amethyst is one of our recommendations but it does not have to be this. You choose! The purpose of this exercise is to clear your 7 physical chakras and open up new channels for the 5D light to pass through you.

 Ensure to clear or activate your crystal before you begin this process. You will know which one to use as it will present itself. If you are unsure, ask your higher self to guide you to it. Stand barefoot on the Earth and place your crystal under your foot so it is connecting both you and the Earth. 

Now, set your intention to draw down "5D Light" through you, into the Earth, for the purpose of anchoring a new golden density of light. Take 12 centering breaths and take your time. With the in breath, imagine your cells becoming more golden and glowing. When you breathe out, release anything of the old not serving you.

After breath number 12, say, "As per the divine blueprint creation laws, I now accept the new energies of the 5th dimension. I AM a channel for this higher light to now move into the Earth."

Next, beginning at your root chakra, move up every chakra spending about 20 seconds on each. Bring your awareness to the chakra, clear, activate and spin it clockwise. Say the words, "cleared", "cleansed", "activated" and then spin it. 

On the final command, spin the chakra clockwise as if a clock dial was face down in front of you. As the chakra picks up speed, imagine it turning golden white. Repeat for all; the root, the sacral, the solar plexus, the heart, the throat, the third eye and the crown.

Observe how you are feeling once you have cleared all seven. Next bring your awareness to your soul star. Using conscious breathing, now allow the golden white light from your higher self to channel from your crown through each chakra deep into Gaia's heart or, the central sun 'Atoma'. 

Stay in this exercise until you feel enough golden energy has anchored into the 5D grids. Be sure to send a love and gratitude to Gaia, your trusted planetary partner in this evolution. We recommend doing this daily or, every few days. Your crystal companion will help amplify and facilitate a new bridge between the 3rd, 4th and 5th density and clear any blocked energy in your field."

snippet.title: "IT'S ABOUT TO GET CRAZY..." - The Pleiadians 2024 | Caylin
snippet.description:
Wow loving this powerful activation, here it is again for anyone that missed it:

*Here’s a simple yet powerful practice to help you connect deeply with your heart center, facilitating a profound sense of love, compassion, and unity with all that is. Find a quiet space, choose a peaceful and comfortable spot where you can sit undisturbed for a few minutes. This could be a favorite corner of your home, a spot in nature, or any place where you feel relaxed and safe.

Set your intention. Before beginning, set a clear intention for this exercise. You might say to yourself or out loud, "I open my heart to receive and give love freely, to connect deeply with my true essence, and to embrace unity with all beings."

Close your eyes and take a few deep, slow breaths. With each inhalation, imagine drawing in peace and calm. With each exhalation, release any tension or discomfort you may be holding. Next, turn your attention to your heart center located in the middle of your chest. Imagine a bright emerald green light glowing in this area. With each breath, see this light becoming brighter and more vibrant.

Now silently or softly chant the spiral or seed mantra for the heart chakra, "Yum." As you repeat this sound, feel the vibration expanding and deepening your connection to love and compassion. Next, visualize the green light from your heart expanding outward, enveloping you in a warm, comforting glow.

Imagine this light extending further, reaching out to your loved ones, your community, and even to those you may have difficulties with. Send them love and gratitude. Now imagine this radiant green light spreading further beyond your immediate surroundings, connecting you with the heart of the Earth, the cosmos, and all living beings. Feel a profound sense of oneness and unconditional love.

Practice this heart chakra activation exercise regularly, especially during times of significant energy shifts, this coming August of your calendar. It will not only aid in opening your heart chakra but also support you in navigating the waves of change with grace, compassion, and a deep sense of interconnectedness with all that is.*
